IT OFFERS A LOVELY DECORATED FORMAL LIVING AND INVITING DINING HOME. THIS LARGE HOME OFFERS HARDWOOD FLOORS, GRANITE COUNTER TOP, STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES WHICH INCLUDE; COOK TOP WITH DOUBLE OVENS, DISHWASHER AND A MICROWAVE. ENJOY MEALS IN THE BREAKFAST AREA WITH A BAY WINDOW AND A VIEW OF THE PRIVATE YARD WITH A PERGOLA READY FOR RELAXING ALL YEAR ROUND; SPRING, SUMMER AND FALL. ENJOY THE SURROUND SOUND ON THE MAIN FLOOR, OWNERS SUITE AND OUTSIDE. GUEST ROOM ON THE MAIN WITH A KING SIZE BED WITH PRIVATE ACCESS TO THE FULL BATHROOM. UPSTAIRS IS A LARGE OWNERS SUITE WITH HIS AND HER CLOSET AND A LUXURIOUS MASTER BATHROOM AND 4 ADDITIONAL BEDROOMS AND 2  FULL BATHS. THIS HOME HAS A LOT TO OFFER!
